{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Myself, since I had difficulties with my feet, they, they wanted me to, to work in the management, in the financial management of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But prior to that, they sent me for an IQ test, to see if, if I'm able to do that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I passed the test satisfactory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was-- they were satisfied with the results.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as a result, they sent me to a business school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a college, a business college, in Haifa, for two years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was working in the, in the management of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as a bookkeeper, I worked in, in, in the office of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was very unhappy, because my friends worked in the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I used to look clean, and they looked dirty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I felt bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after negotiating with the kibbutz for a while, they let me work during the harvest time in the agriculture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- to prove, to prove my capabilities, my friends taught me quietly how to drive the tractors and the truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they finally took me out on a test, I-- they didn't have to show me anything, because I, I knew, I knew what to do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was-- we lived there from '46, till just prior to the War of Independence in 1948.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were trained secretly, because the British were still controlling Israel, to use various type of weapons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and we were taught judo and whatever it, whatever it requires.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the entire group, we joined the, the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not only did we join the Haganah, we joined the commando group, which used to be called the Palmach.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was like the crown jewel of the Jewish defense forces.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
